{
  "texts": [
    "This method could obtain more acoustic features of Uyghur.",
    "The Chinese DSR based on HMM-GMM performs well for a large vocabulary recognition system.",
    "Li and Meng (2012) built a Tibetan Lhasa recognition system based on GMM-HMM.",
    "They used the Tibetan phonemes and vowels as acoustic modeling units.",
    "The experiment result showed that this model has a better recognition accuracy for vowels."
  ]
}